{"data":[{"name":"82:1","price":"When the sky breaks apart.","arabic":"إِذَا ٱلسَّمَآءُ ٱنفَطَرَتۡ","category":["82 (Al-Infitar)","Al-Infitar","Surah Al-Infitar"],"ayahNumber":5830,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"82:2","price":"and when the stars fall, scattered,","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلۡكَوَاكِبُ ٱنتَثَرَتۡ","category":["82 (Al-Infitar)","Al-Infitar","Surah Al-Infitar"],"ayahNumber":5831,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"82:3","price":"and when the seas burst forth,","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلۡبِحَارُ فُجِّرَتۡ","category":["82 (Al-Infitar)","Al-Infitar","Surah Al-Infitar"],"ayahNumber":5832,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"82:4","price":"and when the graves are overturned,","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلۡقُبُورُ بُعۡثِرَتۡ","category":["82 (Al-Infitar)","Al-Infitar","Surah Al-Infitar"],"ayahNumber":5833,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"82:5","price":"then each soul will come to know what it has done or what it has left undone.","arabic":"عَلِمَتۡ نَفۡسٞ مَّا قَدَّمَتۡ وَأَخَّرَتۡ","category":["82 (Al-Infitar)","Al-Infitar","Surah Al-Infitar"],"ayahNumber":5834,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"82:6","price":"O mankind, what has lured you away from your Lord, the Most Generous,","arabic":"يَٰٓأَيُّهَا ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ مَا غَرَّكَ بِرَبِّكَ ٱلۡكَرِيمِ","category":["82 (Al-Infitar)","Al-Infitar","Surah Al-Infitar"],"ayahNumber":5835,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"82:7","price":"Who created you, then shaped and proportioned you,","arabic":"ٱلَّذِي خَلَقَكَ فَسَوَّىٰكَ فَعَدَلَكَ","category":["82 (Al-Infitar)","Al-Infitar","Surah Al-Infitar"],"ayahNumber":5836,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"82:8","price":"and assembled you in whatever form He willed?","arabic":"فِيٓ أَيِّ صُورَةٖ مَّا شَآءَ رَكَّبَكَ","category":["82 (Al-Infitar)","Al-Infitar","Surah Al-Infitar"],"ayahNumber":5837,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"82:9","price":"No indeed; but you deny the Judgment Day,","arabic":"كَلَّا بَلۡ تُكَذِّبُونَ بِٱلدِّينِ","category":["82 (Al-Infitar)","Al-Infitar","Surah Al-Infitar"],"ayahNumber":5838,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"82:10","price":"while there are watchers[1] over you,","arabic":"وَإِنَّ عَلَيۡكُمۡ لَحَٰفِظِينَ","category":["82 (Al-Infitar)","Al-Infitar","Surah Al-Infitar"],"ayahNumber":5839,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[1] i.e., angels who preserve all your deeds.","lang":"en"},{"name":"82:11","price":"honorable scribes,","arabic":"كِرَامٗا كَٰتِبِينَ","category":["82 (Al-Infitar)","Al-Infitar","Surah Al-Infitar"],"ayahNumber":5840,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"82:12","price":"who know whatever you do.","arabic":"يَعۡلَمُونَ مَا تَفۡعَلُونَ","category":["82 (Al-Infitar)","Al-Infitar","Surah Al-Infitar"],"ayahNumber":5841,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"82:13","price":"Indeed, the righteous will be in Bliss,","arabic":"إِنَّ ٱلۡأَبۡرَارَ لَفِي نَعِيمٖ","category":["82 (Al-Infitar)","Al-Infitar","Surah Al-Infitar"],"ayahNumber":5842,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"82:14","price":"and the wicked will be in Blazing Fire,","arabic":"وَإِنَّ ٱلۡفُجَّارَ لَفِي جَحِيمٖ","category":["82 (Al-Infitar)","Al-Infitar","Surah Al-Infitar"],"ayahNumber":5843,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"82:15","price":"which they will enter on Judgment Day,","arabic":"يَصۡلَوۡنَهَا يَوۡمَ ٱلدِّينِ","category":["82 (Al-Infitar)","Al-Infitar","Surah Al-Infitar"],"ayahNumber":5844,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"82:16","price":"and will never come out of it.","arabic":"وَمَا هُمۡ عَنۡهَا بِغَآئِبِينَ","category":["82 (Al-Infitar)","Al-Infitar","Surah Al-Infitar"],"ayahNumber":5845,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"82:17","price":"How do you know what Judgment Day is?","arabic":"وَمَآ أَدۡرَىٰكَ مَا يَوۡمُ ٱلدِّينِ","category":["82 (Al-Infitar)","Al-Infitar","Surah Al-Infitar"],"ayahNumber":5846,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"82:18","price":"Again, how do you know what Judgment Day is?","arabic":"ثُمَّ مَآ أَدۡرَىٰكَ مَا يَوۡمُ ٱلدِّينِ","category":["82 (Al-Infitar)","Al-Infitar","Surah Al-Infitar"],"ayahNumber":5847,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"82:19","price":"It is the Day when no soul will be of any help to another, and all command on that Day will be with Allah.","arabic":"يَوۡمَ لَا تَمۡلِكُ نَفۡسٞ لِّنَفۡسٖ شَيۡـٔٗاۖ وَٱلۡأَمۡرُ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لِّلَّهِ","category":["82 (Al-Infitar)","Al-Infitar","Surah Al-Infitar"],"ayahNumber":5848,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"}],"chapter":["82 (Al-Infitar)","Al-Infitar","Surah Al-Infitar","Chapter Al-Infitar","Infitar","Surah Infitar","Chapter Infitar","Al Infitar","Surah Al Infitar","Chapter Al Infitar","Surah 82","Chapter 82","The Cleaving","الإنفطار"]}